243
00:14:07,812 --> 00:14:08,829
Allez-y.

244
00:14:08,999 --> 00:14:11,177
Je regarde mon père
qui essaie de tirer son coup.

245
00:14:12,138 --> 00:14:13,138
Écoutez...

246
00:14:13,501 --> 00:14:15,769
